title: Good Karma Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Catering, Indo-Persian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Good Karma Restaurant has a relaxed, family-friendly atmosphere. Offers several vegan and vegetarian entree options. Half of the menu is dedicated to serving vegan dietary requirements as well as gluten-free diets. Vegan items include kebabs and curries. All appetizers are vegan or vegetarian. Try the eggplant dip and the South Indian butternut squash soup. They carry their own line of foods named Instant Karma.
